    "media:imagetext": "LOS ANGELES (Burbank) - SAN FRANCISCO - OAKLAND\nEffective December 15, 1949 through January 11, 1950\nRead Down\nFLIGHT NUMBERS\nNORTHBOUND\nLos Angeles. PST. Lv\n(BURBANK)\nSan Francisco... Ar\nSan Francisco\nOakland\nAr\n402\n8:00\n9:48\n10:05\n10:20\n416\n432\n• 2416\n12:30\n7:00\n3:30\n2:18\n2:35\n2:50\n8:48\n9:00\n9:15\n5:18\n5:35\n5:50\nNow you can fly between Los\nAngeles and San Francisco or\nOakland for the lowest\nfares\nwith the highest standards of\nsafety, regularity,\nand con-\nvenience... in DC-4 Coach-\nmasters, chartered from and\noperated by Western Air Lines,\nAmerica's Oldest Certificated\nAirline:\nRead Down'\nSOUTHBOUND\nOakland ....PST. Lv\nSan Francisco ....Ar\nSan Francisco\nLv\nLos Angeles .\n(BURBANK)\n.Ar\n403\n8:30\n8:45\n9:00\n10:48\nFLIGHT NUMBERS\n417\n433\n12:30\n7:15\n12:45\n7:30\n1:00\n7:45\n2:48\n9:33\nSubject to change without notice\n• Operates Fridays\nand Sundays only.\n• 2417\n3:15\n3:30\n3:45\n5:33\nA.M.— Light Figures\nP.M. —Dark Figures\nFOR INTRA-STATE TRAFFIC ONLY\nWESTERN AIR LINES OF CALIFORNIA, INC,\nDaily DC-4\nCoachmaster\nflights between\nLOS ANGELES\n(Burbank)\nSAN FRANCISCO\nOAKLAND\nonly\n5095",
